                            oc:hasContent [ a oc:CodeExample ;
                                    oc:blockType "code_block" ;
                                    oc:codeContent """---
name: warn-env-file-edits
enabled: true
event: file
conditions:
  - field: file_path
    operator: regex_match
    pattern: \\.env$
  - field: new_text
    operator: contains
    pattern: API_KEY
---

You're adding an API key to a .env file. Ensure this file is in .gitignore!
""" ;
